{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "pinteria-api-collection-v2",
    "name": "Pinteria API v2",
    "description": "Dokumentasi API Pinteria — Platform Edukasi Inklusi Anak Difabel (SDG #4 Quality Education)\n\n## Metode Autentikasi\n1. **JWT Bearer** — POST /api/login → gunakan token di header `Authorization: Bearer <token>`\n2. **Basic Auth** — POST /api/login/basic → header `Authorization: Basic base64(email:password)`\n3. **API Key** — header `X-API-Key: skillbridge-api-key-2024-secret`\n\n## Cara Pakai\n1. Jalankan Register atau Login → token otomatis tersimpan ke `{{jwt_token}}`\n2. Semua endpoint protected langsung bisa diuji\n3. Untuk API Key, variable `{{api_key}}` sudah terisi otomatis",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "http://skill_bridge.test/api", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "jwt_token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "api_key", "value": "skillbridge-api-key-2024-secret", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "child_id", "value": "1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "lesson_id", "value": "1", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "session_id", "value": "1", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{jwt_token}}", "type": "string" }]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "🔐 1. Autentikasi",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('jwt_token', res.token);",
                  "    pm.test('Register berhasil dan token tersedia', () => {",
                  "        pm.expect(res).to.have.property('token');",
                  "        pm.expect(res.message).to.equal('Registrasi berhasil.');",
                  "    });",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Orang Tua Contoh\",\n  \"email\": \"orangtua@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\",\n  \"password_confirmation\": \"password123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/register",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["register"]
            },
            "description": "Mendaftarkan akun orang tua baru (role: parent). Mengembalikan JWT token di field `token` (bukan `access_token`).\n\nValidasi:\n- name: required, maks 255 karakter\n- email: required, unik\n- password: required, min 8 karakter, harus cocok dengan password_confirmation"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (JWT Bearer)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('jwt_token', res.access_token);",
                  "    pm.test('Login berhasil dan token tersedia', () => {",
                  "        pm.expect(res).to.have.property('access_token');",
                  "        pm.expect(res.token_type).to.equal('bearer');",
                  "    });",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"orangtua@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["login"]
            },
            "description": "Login dengan email dan password. Mengembalikan JWT Bearer token di field `access_token`.\n\nGunakan token di header: Authorization: Bearer <access_token>"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login (Basic Auth)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('jwt_token', res.access_token);",
                  "    pm.test('Basic Auth login berhasil', () => pm.expect(res).to.have.property('access_token'));",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "basic",
              "basic": [
                { "key": "username", "value": "orangtua@example.com", "type": "string" },
                { "key": "password", "value": "password123", "type": "string" }
              ]
            },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/login/basic",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["login", "basic"]
            },
            "description": "Login menggunakan HTTP Basic Authentication.\nKirim kredensial di header: Authorization: Basic base64(email:password)\n\nContoh: base64('user@test.com:pass123') = dXNlckB0ZXN0LmNvbTpwYXNzMTIz\nHeader: Authorization: Basic dXNlckB0ZXN0LmNvbTpwYXNzMTIz\n\nJika credentials kosong, server mengembalikan 401 + header WWW-Authenticate."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('jwt_token', res.access_token);",
                  "    pm.test('Token berhasil diperbarui', () => pm.expect(res).to.have.property('access_token'));",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{jwt_token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/refresh",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["refresh"]
            },
            "description": "Memperbarui JWT token sebelum kedaluwarsa. Token lama akan di-invalidate dan diganti token baru. Token baru otomatis tersimpan ke {{jwt_token}}."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get User (Me)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{jwt_token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/me",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["me"]
            },
            "description": "Mendapatkan data pengguna yang sedang login beserta daftar anak (relasi children di-eager load).\n\nResponse: { user: { id, name, email, role, children: [...] } }"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{jwt_token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/logout",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["logout"]
            },
            "description": "Membatalkan (invalidate) JWT token aktif. Setelah ini token tidak bisa digunakan lagi."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "🔑 2. API Key (Publik)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Lessons Publik (via API Key)",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "X-API-Key", "value": "{{api_key}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/public/lessons",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["public", "lessons"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "tipe_dunia", "value": "audio", "description": "Filter: audio (tunanetra) atau visual (tunarungu)", "disabled": true }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Mendapatkan daftar lesson tanpa JWT login. Hanya metadata (tanpa field media).\n\nHeader wajib: X-API-Key: skillbridge-api-key-2024-secret\nQuery opsional: ?tipe_dunia=audio|visual\n\nResponse 403 jika API Key salah."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Modules Publik (via API Key)",
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "X-API-Key", "value": "{{api_key}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/public/modules?child_id={{child_id}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["public", "modules"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "child_id", "value": "{{child_id}}", "description": "ID anak (wajib)" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Mendapatkan modul berdasarkan profil anak (usia & jenis disabilitas).\n\nQuery wajib: ?child_id=<id>\nResponse: { usia, jenis_disabilitas, modules: [...] }"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "👶 3. Children (Manajemen Data Anak)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Daftar Children",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{jwt_token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/children",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["children"]
            },
            "description": "Mendapatkan semua anak milik orang tua yang sedang login.\nResponse: { children: [{id, user_id, nama_panggilan, tanggal_lahir, jenis_disabilitas, ...}] }"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Tambah Child",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('child_id', res.child.id.toString());",
                  "    pm.test('Anak berhasil ditambahkan', () => pm.expect(res.message).to.equal('Anak berhasil ditambahkan.'));",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{jwt_token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nama_panggilan\": \"Budi\",\n  \"tanggal_lahir\": \"2019-05-10\",\n  \"jenis_disabilitas\": \"tunanetra\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/children",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["children"]
            },
            "description": "Menambahkan data anak baru.\n\nValidasi:\n- nama_panggilan: required, maks 100 karakter\n- tanggal_lahir: required, format date\n- jenis_disabilitas: required, enum: tunanetra | tunarungu\n\nNilai jenis_disabilitas:\n- tunanetra → Audio World (belajar via suara)\n- tunarungu → Visual World (belajar via gambar)\n\nID anak baru otomatis tersimpan ke {{child_id}}."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Detail Child",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{jwt_token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/children/{{child_id}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["children", "{{child_id}}"]
            },
            "description": "Detail satu anak beserta relasi lesson_completions dan quiz_results.\nMengembalikan 403 jika anak bukan milik orang tua yang login."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Child",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{jwt_token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nama_panggilan\": \"Budi Santoso\",\n  \"jenis_disabilitas\": \"tunarungu\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/children/{{child_id}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["children", "{{child_id}}"]
            },
            "description": "Memperbarui data anak. Semua field bersifat opsional (partial update menggunakan 'sometimes').\nMengembalikan 403 jika anak bukan milik orang tua yang login."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Hapus Child",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{jwt_token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/children/{{child_id}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["children", "{{child_id}}"]
            },
            "description": "Menghapus data anak. Mengembalikan 403 jika anak bukan milik orang tua yang login."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "📊 4. Dashboard Orang Tua",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Dashboard Utama (Semua Anak)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{jwt_token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/dashboard",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["dashboard"]
            },
            "description": "Ringkasan aktivitas belajar semua anak.\nResponse: { children: [{id, nama_panggilan, jenis_disabilitas, total_lesson_selesai, rata_rata_skor, total_waktu_belajar_menit}] }"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Progress Detail Per Anak",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{jwt_token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/dashboard/child/{{child_id}}?days=30",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["dashboard", "child", "{{child_id}}"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "days", "value": "30", "description": "Jumlah hari ke belakang (default: 30)" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Progress detail satu anak dalam rentang waktu tertentu.\n\nQuery opsional: ?days=30 (default 30 hari)\n\nResponse berisi:\n- summary: total lesson, rata skor, total waktu belajar\n- charts: data Chart.js-ready (labels, lessons_completed, quiz_scores, study_time_minutes)\n\nMengembalikan 403 jika anak bukan milik orang tua yang login."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "📚 5. Lessons",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Daftar Lessons (Metadata Only)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{jwt_token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/lessons",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["lessons"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "tipe_dunia", "value": "audio", "description": "Filter: audio (tunanetra) atau visual (tunarungu)", "disabled": true }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Daftar lesson hanya metadata (tanpa field media: gambar, audio_story_url, dll) untuk efisiensi lazy loading.\n\nHanya lesson dengan aktif=true yang dikembalikan.\nUrut berdasarkan field 'urutan'."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Detail Lesson (+ Quiz Questions)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (res.lesson && res.lesson.quiz_questions && res.lesson.quiz_questions.length > 0) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('quiz_question_id', res.lesson.quiz_questions[0].id.toString());",
                  "    }",
                  "    pm.test('Lesson berhasil dimuat dengan quiz_questions', () => {",
                  "        pm.expect(res.lesson).to.have.property('quiz_questions');",
                  "    });",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{jwt_token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/lessons/{{lesson_id}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["lessons", "{{lesson_id}}"]
            },
            "description": "Detail lengkap satu lesson termasuk semua field media dan soal quiz.\n\nResponse berisi semua field lesson + quiz_questions[]:\n- tipe soal: pilihan_ganda, audio, drag_drop\n- pilihan: array JSON\n- audio_url, gambar, animasi_url (media per soal)\n\nID quiz_question pertama otomatis tersimpan ke {{quiz_question_id}}."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Selesaikan Lesson",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{jwt_token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"child_id\": {{child_id}}\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/lessons/{{lesson_id}}/complete",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["lessons", "{{lesson_id}}", "complete"]
            },
            "description": "Menandai lesson sebagai selesai untuk anak tertentu.\nMenggunakan firstOrCreate — aman dipanggil berulang kali (idempotent)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Mulai Sesi Belajar",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('session_id', res.session_id.toString());",
                  "    pm.test('Sesi belajar dimulai', () => pm.expect(res).to.have.property('session_id'));",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{jwt_token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"child_id\": {{child_id}}\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/lessons/{{lesson_id}}/start-session",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["lessons", "{{lesson_id}}", "start-session"]
            },
            "description": "Memulai sesi belajar. Dipanggil saat anak memasuki halaman lesson.\nResponse: { message, session_id }\n\nsession_id otomatis tersimpan ke {{session_id}} untuk digunakan di endpoint End Session."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Akhiri Sesi Belajar",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{jwt_token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/sessions/{{session_id}}/end",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["sessions", "{{session_id}}", "end"]
            },
            "description": "Mengakhiri sesi belajar. Durasi dihitung otomatis dari started_at hingga sekarang.\nResponse: { message, durasi_detik }\n\nGunakan session_id dari response endpoint 'Mulai Sesi Belajar'."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "🧩 6. Quiz",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Kirim Jawaban Quiz",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{jwt_token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"child_id\": {{child_id}},\n  \"lesson_id\": {{lesson_id}},\n  \"quiz_question_id\": 1,\n  \"jawaban_anak\": \"A\",\n  \"benar\": true,\n  \"skor\": 100,\n  \"percobaan\": 1\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/quiz/answer",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["quiz", "answer"]
            },
            "description": "Mengirimkan jawaban quiz anak. Setiap jawaban disimpan sebagai record terpisah.\n\nValidasi:\n- child_id: required, exists:children\n- lesson_id: required, exists:lessons\n- quiz_question_id: required, exists:quiz_questions\n- jawaban_anak: required, string\n- benar: required, boolean\n- skor: required, integer 0-100\n- percobaan: required, integer >= 1\n\nResponse 201: { message, result: { id, ...semua field jawaban } }"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Hasil Quiz Per Lesson",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{jwt_token}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/quiz/results?child_id={{child_id}}&lesson_id={{lesson_id}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["quiz", "results"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "child_id", "value": "{{child_id}}", "description": "ID anak (wajib)" },
                { "key": "lesson_id", "value": "{{lesson_id}}", "description": "ID lesson (wajib)" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Mendapatkan semua hasil quiz anak untuk lesson tertentu.\n\nQuery wajib: ?child_id=X&lesson_id=Y\n\nResponse: { results: [{ ...quiz_result, quiz_question: { pertanyaan, jawaban_benar, pilihan, tipe, poin } }] }\n\nRelasi quiz_question di-eager load otomatis."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
